1
00:00:11,280 --> 00:00:13,720
-(INDISTINCT WHISPERING)
-Stop it!

2
00:00:13,800 --> 00:00:17,440
Stop it! Stop whispering!

3
00:00:17,520 --> 00:00:18,520
Stop!

4
00:00:19,240 --> 00:00:21,080
(WHISPERING STOPS)

5
00:00:24,440 --> 00:00:25,520
(SIGHS)

6
00:00:26,560 --> 00:00:27,720
(SHOUTS)

7
00:00:28,640 --> 00:00:29,760
(BREATHING HEAVILY)

8
00:00:30,120 --> 00:00:31,240
Leave me alone!

9
00:00:31,760 --> 00:00:32,880
You're not real!

10
00:00:33,200 --> 00:00:34,960
I know you're not real.

11
00:00:35,360 --> 00:00:38,040
You're just voices inside my head.

12
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:40,400
Leave me alone!

13
00:00:50,360 --> 00:00:51,840
(SNARLING)

14
00:00:56,120 --> 00:00:59,280
What do you want from me, hmm?

15
00:00:59,360 --> 00:01:00,920
The Doctor.

16
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:03,320
What are you talking about?
I don't understand.

17
00:01:03,440 --> 00:01:04,880
Do you want to live?

18
00:01:05,360 --> 00:01:06,720
You can save me?

19
00:01:06,920 --> 00:01:09,040
We can give you information.

20
00:01:09,120 --> 00:01:12,960
These symbols. You will memorise them.

21
00:01:13,800 --> 00:01:14,840
I don't...

22
00:01:15,640 --> 00:01:18,200
(GROANING)

23
00:01:19,600 --> 00:01:22,600
Their meaning and purpose
ls now within your mind.

24
00:01:22,760 --> 00:01:26,280
You will give this information
to the reptile detective.

25
00:01:26,360 --> 00:01:27,880
What kind of men are you?

26
00:01:27,960 --> 00:01:30,680
We are not men. We are the Intelligence.

27
00:01:30,760 --> 00:01:32,640
All of time and space is known to us.

28
00:01:32,720 --> 00:01:35,080
Will this save me? Huh?

29
00:01:36,160 --> 00:01:38,040
WillL I still hang tomorrow?

30
00:01:38,120 --> 00:01:39,480
A pardon will be yours.

31
00:01:39,560 --> 00:01:41,320
The rope will not.

32
00:01:42,600 --> 00:01:44,800
Will you finally leave me alone?

33
00:01:44,880 --> 00:01:47,000
You will live a good, long life.

34
00:01:47,080 --> 00:01:51,400
Except you will always have
such trouble sleeping.

35
00:01:52,680 --> 00:01:54,600
No. No!

36
00:01:54,720 --> 00:01:55,720
(SNARLING)

37
00:01:55,800 --> 00:01:57,040
You leave me alone.

38
00:01:57,880 --> 00:02:00,600
Leave me alone! You are not real!

